subject: Hockey, Ice
lead_paragraph: Jacob Josefson scored the lone goal in the shootout, and Cory Schneider made it stand up as the host Devils ended their tiebreaker frustration with a come-from-behind 2-1 victory over the Winnipeg Jets.
